relevance_user_prompt_template:
Return JSON with keys: relevant (bool), matched_topics (list[str]), cooling_level (str: chip-level|board-level|system-level|unknown), cooling_methodology (str), rationale (str, <=40 words). Use both title and abstract.
Topics: {topics_json}
Cooling taxonomy: {cooling_taxonomy_json}
Title: {title}
Abstract: {abstract}

analysis_user_prompt_template:
Write sections: 'Topic-Focused Collaboration Analysis' and 'Actionable Next Steps'. Focus on collaboration patterns emerging from relevant papers and topics.
Input topics: {topics_json}
Relevant paper count: {relevant_count}
Topic stats: {stats_json}
Paper sample: {paper_sample_json}
